            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2f,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "(A Machine Box... Harol might know about things like this...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "What's wrong, Sophie? Why are you just staring at me?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x44,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Oh, um. Can you take a look at this?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "What's this...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x3,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x26,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "Showed Harol the \"Machine Box\"."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "I thought you might know what this is."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Hm... I do know what it is, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2a,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Really!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Yeah, but it's broken in all kinds of places. It's also missing some parts. It won't work like this."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x21,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Uu, I see... And the switch won't move, either..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x23,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "...Um, Harol? Do you think you can fix it?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Give me a second..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "I think I can repair it. But I can't replace the missing parts..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "...Then can you tell me what parts are missing?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Why?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "I could make them with alchemy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "...You really can do anything with alchemy, can't you? Just give me a minute."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x44,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "This should be everything that's missing."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Thank you, Harol! I'll go make them real fast."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Sure. I won't be expecting anything, though."
        }
    ]
